fields.name: o_acx_catastrophe_row_md5checksum
fields.expression:
MD5('id'|| id ||'update_count' || update_count ||'update_user' || update_user ||'update_timestamp' || update_timestamp ||
'catastrophe_yr' || catastrophe_yr ||'catastrophe_number' || catastrophe_number ||'description' || description ||
'start_dt' || start_dt ||
'start_tm' || start_tm ||
'end_dt' || end_dt ||
'end_tm' || end_tm ||
'status_cd' || status_cd ||'event_type' || event_type)

object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
select distinct 
cb.batch_id,
metal_ac.source_name, metal_ac.load_type, metal_ac.system_id, metal_ac.parent_id, metal_ac.cmm_container, metal_ac.id, metal_ac.update_count, 
metal_ac.update_user, metal_ac.update_timestamp, metal_ac.catastrophe_yr, metal_ac.catastrophe_number, metal_ac.description, metal_ac.start_tm, metal_ac.end_tm, metal_ac.status_cd, metal_ac.row_id, metal_ac.event_type, bronze_dr.acx_catastrophe_row_id,bronze_dr.acx_catastrophe_row_md5checksum, metal_ac.start_dt, metal_ac.end_dt
FROM $$raw_schema.acx_catastrophe metal_ac
LEFT JOIN $$staging_schema.acx_catastrophe bronze_dr
    ON CAST(TRIM(metal_ac.system_id) AS INT) = CAST(bronze_dr.system_id AS INT)
   AND COALESCE(TRIM(metal_ac.cmm_container), '') = COALESCE(bronze_dr.cmm_container, '')
   AND bronze_dr.acx_catastrophe_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
   AND bronze_dr.acx_catastrophe_row_status = 'Active'
CROSS JOIN current_batch cb
ORDER BY 
    metal_ac.system_id,
    metal_ac.cmm_container,
    metal_ac.id;
